Reviewed-by: Thierry Reding <thierry.reding@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Joao Pinto <jpinto@synopsys.com>
Tested-by: Corentin Labbe <clabbe.montjoie@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: David S. Miller <davem@davemloft.net>

